{"type": "article", "id": 43319, "title": "Marie Claire 创始人逝世，以及，“世界最小制鞋工厂”在日本开张 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-07-24T03:21:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 17717, "name": "Keen"}, {"id": 1912, "name": "Marie Claire"}, {"id": 2636, "name": "Swatch"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170724110301wknOChebA5WElVFH.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/business-features/swatch-first-half-sales-raise-specter-of-sector-improvement-10950928/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Swatch 发布上半年财报，净利润增长 7.6%</strong></a> | Swatch 集团发布上半年财报，按不变汇率计算，集团销售额上涨 1.2 ％。其中，净利润同比上涨 7.6％ 至 2.81 亿瑞士法郎，销售额则下降 0.3％ 至 37.1 亿瑞士法郎。另外，珠宝手表部门的销售额达 35.8 亿瑞士法郎。该集团表示不会因行业低迷而裁员或降薪，未来一年内还将新增 100 至 120 家门店。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/media/marie-claire-founder-evelyne-prouvost-dies-at-10950445/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>时尚杂志&nbsp;Marie Claire 的女创始人逝世，享年 78 岁</strong></a> | 上周四，Évelyne Prouvost 因一场自行车事故不幸逝世，享年 78 岁。时尚杂志 Marie Claire 在 1937 年由 Évelyne Prouvost 的祖父、法国商人 Jean Prouvost 首次推出，因为二战而停刊了一阵。Évelyne Prouvost 于 1973 年推出了 Cosmopolitan，又在 1976 年买回了 Marie Claire。现在，Marie Claire 旗下包括 12 种杂志。<br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/prada-cloudbust-sneaker\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada 带来了全新的 Cloudbust 球鞋系列</a>，这双鞋采用了无鞋带式的一脚蹬，鞋身布满网眼，中部有 Prada logo 的细搭带固定。这次率先发布的三双女生配色将于 8 月份上架，男生版会在 11 月份登场。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105218KWxDPbe1OJoq2c96.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105218WpT8cyR04uCQiNG6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105218hnYgls5FcWT6O4uN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105211D4C6YGIFOPaeVUxn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105211BcApWqa6wrmT1juf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105210huQGxZPeLnO2o5ND.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105211jyP3iVOhUG9TAs1S.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105210ISqnjx3VU5yL4uKo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105210mLfjRzye3h0Crd4q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/vetements-2017-fall-winter-first-delivery-dsml\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vetements 在伦敦 Dover Street Market 店发布了 2017 秋冬系列首波新品</a>。包括连帽衫、T 恤等多种单品，还有与 Swarovski、Levi’s、Mackintosh、Brioni、Reebok、Alpha Industries 及 Eastpak 等品牌的联名标志。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105319OPkJvIDLmFzESBQf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105319KpfQFm7sc4H98rRd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105319YuqgFvWR0J6ridSX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105319JIKEeGkfhjclZTBw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105319Nc0qUl3t8MErDZwm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241053203bi1SWuQxzDlN4UI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105320D90A4NLtQ3cuVgwh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105320FHgpYP6ul5tL1DyQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105321yLid7CHYGSFWnsRQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105321KXJvIWhtmYFzafB8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105321ofxk3KhyN12jXdvL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105321D36HWPMEpsL7iCc2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105322xVmr4ZKXhSCoagc9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105321Q7Tq4NbYUXFhvefk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105322YaBiC0rTR5oh79Vp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241053225cDOGw8YdibluPRt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105322A83O7HN9bZtKUGE0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105323b1QSJjkqPE0x7C6c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105323D0I4pOzRECg2Vc1n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105323EfkPu2jARZdOMgtL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105324BXekVZ47RxFTW0fD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105324MwErOIhWCXTvHyP3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105324XEWyDq1cYQa2kf0K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/07/21/marc-newson-designs-limited-edition-brandy-bottle-hennessy-xo-cognac/\" rel=\"nofollow\">工业设计师 Marc Newson 为轩尼诗 X.O 设计了新的限量版瓶子</a>。与之前 X.O 的葡萄藤纹瓶子相比，Newson 给 X.O 的瓶身换上了直线条，另外还专门为它设计了一个特定的塑料透明礼盒，整体造型更具现代性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105424bEpiQPgRy6d8O1Mk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105442tKdC3BIcPOSHXgLG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.555415\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105441dTDYoNI62ZXfR3gE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.582064\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Milliennial Pink，千禧粉色最近有点火。Nike 也顺势推出了&nbsp;<a href=\"http://store.nike.com/us/en_us/pw/chrome-blush/ukv\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chrome Blush </a>的粉色系列，包括一系列运动内衣、背心、卫衣、球鞋等单品，你觉得好看嘛？ </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241055119T0JDY51ozHaWGCE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.748750\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241055239HjkDcMIhWfPyL7X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105523J92gSpYktfzGWIZC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105523DTtEnLcHReO7rFph.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105524GLwoOsHa9WRJ62y1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105524pnF3S7kMWoIQLTev.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105524D2PYKniqVszUpSxe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105524OHIiwcq5ZrYDlSda.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105524QhYHDO9fwnmLlx6G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105525IvrVguG97J321hCf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105525hMoaUJQxdD8uWRjt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105526odc0VlxfvjL2p7qE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105526dCZgpVmy7kEwxXnF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105525fRehSdvCYbrPtBQA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105527AfVrv8qZ6mTKgEJC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105526TceIX7OBpJCYru3V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105528eaDSMghdp1Jz9HRy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>刚刚过去的周末，美国户外潮鞋品牌 KEEN 在东京原宿开了一家“<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/452022\" rel=\"nofollow\">世界上最小的制鞋工厂</a>”。店内，有最新型 UNEEK （两根绳和鞋底构成的户外凉鞋）机器人，可以现场选择颜色、柔软程度等定制鞋子，结合现场的 DJ 音乐、艺术家长场雄和万美的作品，消费者可以观看机器人制鞋的全过程，还挺有趣的。<br></p><p>这家小球鞋工厂只在 7 月 21 日至 23 日开放，现已关闭。不过，据 KEEN 品牌所称，UNEEK 机器人技术可能会在未来大规模的运用，可以期待一下。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105552JysLNVO4faDAqSx7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241055516zeHYBKFR8pnrhDG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.561667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/alexander-wang-2017-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexander Wang 发布了 2017 秋冬系列 lookbook</a>。这一季男装以 80 年代的汽车广告、Steven King 书籍封面、闪电印花为灵感，包括针织帽、皮革外套、印花 T 恤等多款单品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105618dQ3eKToX4Yg78Lx2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105618UPu1AIes7SkmBzTr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105619TUvbD04WPOfSHly1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105619PVz4SiMO8XLUkF1m.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105619AvYq6bMlt80EPGRW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105620yJYi2Tp35mMRx1hQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105620bx5itIeZPqQV8voY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105620IE3QvFwRoMiVP02a.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241056219yuKTq3eopWRzCXn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105621eth4fuLiF1z9Acsg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105621FX7x9lcSeWboNqa3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105622Mcw2UhWaPi8oAvLj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105622gflbKW7pMokV9ROu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241056222gmelcWEyTMS9riD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105623B8yG2FOTt9sV7cZn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105622oFIvVzlaqej0y9w3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105623T7Hl3OIY5mqSEbBh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241056231OqVincRGzDSQJym.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241056240iYqXorVEjyUmdpZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105623PdJc2xWwF9RCV6E5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724105624engpQDrbHZTjWqIy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Nike</p>"}